This paper is about road defect detection using computer vision and deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also uses unsupervised learning and adversarial learning, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves image processing and signal processing, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
